name: DataHIS
summary: s component lets you create a query by entering a search keyword, bounding box, start date, stop date, etc. Once data has been downloaded from the web service, it can either be saved to files or accessed directly by other components through the
port, which has a standard CSDMS IRF-based interface. Note that this component must currently be used in
mode, so that the Run button will appear.
author: Scott D. Peckham
